<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,251,1816,1840]" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">MAP 21.</emphasis>
Collecting localities of 
<emphasis box="[508,680,1817,1840]" italics="true" pageId="27" pageNumber="28">
<taxonomicName box="[508,676,1817,1840]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Polia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" phylum="Nemertea" rank="species" species="imbrifera">Polia imbrifera</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
