<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1436,152,700]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,376,562,588]" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Larval hosts:</emphasis>
This species is somewhat polyphagous on woody shrubs and trees. Hosts include chokecherry (
<taxonomicName box="[316,534,600,625]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Prunus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="virginiana">
<emphasis box="[316,534,600,625]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Prunus virginiana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L., 
<taxonomicName box="[584,701,600,626]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Rosaceae</taxonomicName>
), willow (
<taxonomicName box="[823,927,600,626]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Salicaceae" genus="Salix" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="undetermined">
<emphasis box="[823,882,600,625]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Salix</emphasis>
sp.
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[941,1072,600,626]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Salicaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Salicaceae</taxonomicName>
), sweet birch (
<taxonomicName box="[1249,1395,600,625]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Betula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lenta">
<emphasis box="[1249,1395,600,625]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Betula lenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L., 
<taxonomicName authorityName="S.F.Gray" authorityYear="1822" box="[151,292,637,663]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Betulaceae</taxonomicName>
), gray birch (
<taxonomicName authority="Marsh." authorityName="Marsh." box="[461,786,637,663]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Betula" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fagales" pageId="28" pageNumber="29" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="populifolia">
<emphasis box="[461,687,637,662]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Betula populifolia</emphasis>
Marsh.
</taxonomicName>
